metadata.name: Invisible Noun Cat #1
metadata.description: Noun Cats - The Invisibles are part one of two nearly identical 5,000 piece collections. Each Invisible has a corresponding Cat in the other set (The Cats). Find your Nounterpart and interact with special smart contracts to create connections, shared experiences, and fun new mints! Noun Cats is a CC0 project: you are free to do whatever you like with them.
